title: CMS candidate Amelia Stinson-Wesley says she has contacts to serve a diverse county
text: Amelia Stinson-Wesley is a first-time candidate seeking a second term on the Charlotte-Mecklenburg school board. When Tim Morgan was elected to an at-large seat four years ago, she applied to fill the remaining two years on his term
